title: Inqalab News | Urdu News App

creator: Breakers
descriptionHtml:
Inqalab News is a personalized news app that organizes and highlights what’s happening in the world so that you can discover more about the stories that matter to you. It keeps you updated with trending news and top stories from across the world.

With Inqalab News, you’ll find:
LOCAL NEWS: Explore your community through stories and articles from news outlets in your local area. Customize and choose multiple locations so that you can know what’s happening near you or wherever your home is.

FULL COVERAGE: Dive deeper into a story with multiple perspectives. The Full coverage feature organizes everything online about a story, surfacing and highlighting coverage from different outlets and media. With just a tap, you’ll uncover how the story is unfolding and how everyone is reporting on it.

STORIES FOR YOU: The For You section delivers personalized news related to your interests. Take control and customize the articles that you see by following the topics and sources that you care about.

ACCESS FROM ANY DEVICE: Inqalab News is designed to meet the needs of users with different phones and levels of connection. When your connection isn’t strong or you need to save data, Inqalab News will continue to work smoothly by slimming down the size of images and downloading fewer data. Articles can be downloaded over Wi-Fi to save and read for later when you are offline.

Inqalab News is the most respected and the most-used news app in the country and is well known for its credible journalism. Owned by Breakers Inc. The Inqalab News offers you up-to-date quality news reports, breaking stories, world headlines, sports articles, and last but not the least, offbeat pieces that give you plenty of diversity in reading. Download Inqalab News Pro and stay in the loop with important updates you wouldn’t want to miss.
Features:
• You’re just a click away from getting the latest news from different beats including Lifestyle, Sports, Cricket, Football, Hockey, Business, Entertainment, Health, Science & Tech, National, International, World, Business, Headlines, Lifestyle, Events, Religion, Foods, Social, Education and much more.
• Latest News
Stay updated with latest news around you. Read news, events and world affairs in one place.

• Dozens of Categories
This app provides dozens of categories, read news articles from your desired category.

• Download News
You can use the download news article feature of this app. After downloading news articles you can read those articles while you do not have an internet connection. You can also download important news articles for reading them later.

• Trending News
We provide a separate section to read trending and most popular news of the current day, current week, and current month.

• News push notification
Get critical, breaking news alerts pushed directly to your home screen.

• Data savings
save up to 80% of your mobile data thanks to our unique turbo engine.

• Offline reading
Download your favourite stories while on Wi-Fi and enjoy your reading later without an internet connection.
